<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-orange);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Survey &amp; Compliance</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Façade and condition surveys, intrusive investigation and fire-strategy review — the front end that gets the specification right before work starts. We assess the existing envelope, document its condition and set the spec the build is delivered to.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Survey &amp; Compliance →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Survey &amp; Compliance,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Façade &amp; condition surveys</li><li>Intrusive investigations</li><li>Fire-strategy review</li><li>EWS1-related remedial works</li><li>Specification &amp; design coordination</li><li>Records &amp; golden-thread documentation</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>Building Safety Act 2022 — higher-risk buildings</li><li>BS 8414 &amp; BR 135 — cladding fire performance</li><li>RICS &amp; relevant survey guidance</li><li>CDM 2015 throughout</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>What does a façade survey involve?</summary><p>We survey the existing envelope, assess its condition and review the fire strategy — including intrusive investigation where needed — then set a traceable specification before any work starts.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you carry out works related to an EWS1 assessment?</summary><p>We deliver the remedial works that an EWS1 process can identify on the external wall system. The EWS1 form itself is signed by a suitably qualified assessor; we scope, specify and deliver the resulting works.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you produce the records needed for the safety case?</summary><p>Yes. We document the survey, specification and works as golden-thread records, giving you a traceable pack for the building's safety case under the Building Safety Act 2022.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/fabric/">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope overview</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/facade-cladding/">Façade &amp; Cladding</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/roofing/">Roofing</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/bsa-remediation/">Buil